item.title: two minutes after 8 hours
item.description: 11:32 Friday 19 May 2017 JST I am the butt of the joke about knowing what to do .. I just spent about 8 hours of trying to figure out why CB app was not showing images. Image server was okay, cloudfront was okay, .. was it the app caching things? I had to dig into the source of the app to discover there is a differently spelled version of CB’s domain name, call it seebee, which was being used.
